comment:
* A collection of constants representing different stages of face enrollment.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: UNKNOWN
variables.comment: * The current enrollment stage is not known.

variables.name: FIRST_FRAME_RECEIVED
variables.comment: * Enrollment has just begun. No action is needed from the user yet.

variables.name: WAITING_FOR_CENTERING
variables.comment: * The user must center their face in the frame.

variables.name: HOLD_STILL_IN_CENTER
variables.comment: * The user must keep their face centered in the frame.

variables.name: ENROLLING_MOVEMENT_1
variables.comment: * The user must follow a first set of movement instructions.

variables.name: ENROLLING_MOVEMENT_2
variables.comment: * The user must follow a second set of movement instructions.

variables.name: ENROLLMENT_FINISHED
variables.comment: * Enrollment has completed. No more action is needed from the user.
